### Model Request

We will keep up with the latest progress of the community, and support more popular algorithms and frameworks. If you have any feature requests, please feel free to leave a comment in [MMPose Roadmap](httpxxx').

## Contributing

We appreciate all contributions to improve MMPose. Please refer to [CONTRIBUTING.md](httpxxx') for the contributing guideline.

## Acknowledgement

MMPose is an open source project that is contributed by researchers and engineers from various colleges and companies.
We appreciate all the contributors who implement their methods or add new features, as well as users who give valuable feedbacks.
We wish that the toolbox and benchmark could serve the growing research community by providing a flexible toolkit to reimplement existing methods and develop their own new models.

